<text><body>
<lb n="0027b23" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0027b24" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0027b25" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1203</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0027b26" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0027056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】享和元年刊長谷寺藏本，原本校異中略符（&M062404;）者秀陽阿闍梨本，（&M062304;）者宣雄比丘本，【甲】大治三年寫東寺三密藏本</note>聖<note n="0027057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無＝不【甲】</note><app n="0027057"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">不</rdg></app>動尊安鎮家國等<note n="0027058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此下甲本有金剛三藏傳五字</note><note n="0027058" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>此下甲本有金剛三藏傳五字</note>法</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0027b27" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0027b28" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0027b2801">爾時毘盧遮那如來。為愍念一切有情。常於
<lb n="0027b29" ed="T"/>煩惱苦海之中。流浪生死不出三界。受眾<note n="0027059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">苦＋（難為受苦）【甲】</note><app n="0027059"><lem wit="【大】">苦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">苦難為受苦</rdg></app>
<pb n="0027c" id="T21.1203.0027c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0027c01" ed="T"/>故。展轉造作無量苦業相續不絕。我為拔濟
<lb n="0027c02" ed="T"/>一切有情。於三界中現威德光明自在之身。
<lb n="0027c03" ed="T"/>號曰不動金剛明王。能與人天安樂利益。安
<lb n="0027c04" ed="T"/>鎮家國<note n="0027060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（令）＋無【甲】</note><app n="0027060"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">令無</rdg></app>衰患。若有國<note n="0027061" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">土＝王&M062303;【原】</note><app n="0027061"><lem wit="【大】">土</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ｂ】">王</rdg></app>多諸災難。日月
<lb n="0027c05" ed="T"/>失度惡星變怪。互相陵逼水旱不調。眾生薄
<lb n="0027c06" ed="T"/>福天龍捨離。遇此之時。不祥競起無有休息
<lb n="0027c07" ed="T"/>穀貴飢凍鬼魅流行。疫病妖邪虎狼殘害。暴
<lb n="0027c08" ed="T"/>風霜雹毒惡虫蝗。怨敵頻興群<note n="0027062" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">君＝臣&M062303;【原】</note><app n="0027062"><lem wit="【大】">君</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ｂ】">臣</rdg></app>背版。多
<lb n="0027c09" ed="T"/>諸盜賊征戰屢興。<note n="0027063" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">處＋（處）&M062303;【原】</note><app n="0027063"><lem wit="【大】">處</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ｂ】">處處</rdg></app>災興相續不絕。其國
<lb n="0027c10" ed="T"/><note n="0027064" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔仁〕－【甲】</note><app n="0027064"><lem wit="【大】">仁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>王。若知有此持明之人。應鎮起大慈悲之
<lb n="0027c11" ed="T"/>心。哀愍國界一切有情。行大明王威德祕法。
<lb n="0027c12" ed="T"/>令諸有情增加福德。起慚愧心離諸苦業。其
<lb n="0027c13" ed="T"/>王爾時生大信樂決定之意。召請如是持明
<lb n="0027c14" ed="T"/>大士。應捨財帛衣服珍玩園林屋宅。象馬車
<pb n="0028a" id="T21.1203.0028a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0028a01" ed="T"/>乘奴婢僕從種種上妙吉祥等物而告之言。
<lb n="0028a02" ed="T"/>我為一切有情及國土不安。仁當為我成就
<lb n="0028a03" ed="T"/>此法。我聞此法威力難思。汝當為我<note n="0028001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">我＝等&M062485;【原】，及&M062485;【原】，為&M062485;【原】，〔我〕－【甲】</note><app n="0028001"><lem wit="【大】">我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0028001" type="rest" place="foot">我＝等&M062485;【原】，及&M062485;【原】，為&M062485;【原】</note>一
<lb n="0028a04" ed="T"/>切有情。速可建立此殊勝法除眾災殃。所要
<lb n="0028a05" ed="T"/>之物當隨意取終不違汝。時持明者受是請
<lb n="0028a06" ed="T"/>已。勿生厭倦。依教修崇。當須清淨造立不動
<lb n="0028a07" ed="T"/><note n="0028002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔尊〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0028002"><lem wit="【大】">尊</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">&lac;</rdg></app>明王形像。及八方天王并其眷屬。如法修
<lb n="0028a08" ed="T"/>造隨其自力。或金或銀乃至銅鐵泥木彩畫。
<lb n="0028a09" ed="T"/>身長八指。其兩臂身俱摩羅相。其身洪滿其
<lb n="0028a10" ed="T"/>色如金。頭髮左垂威容極忿。右持智劍左執
<lb n="0028a11" ed="T"/>&CB00559;索。坐金盤石光焰熾然。其焰多有<note n="0028003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">伽＝迦&M062403;【原】＊</note><app n="0028003"><lem wit="【大】">伽</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">迦</rdg></app>樓
<lb n="0028a12" ed="T"/>羅狀。此之形像王宮中置。乃至百官黎庶人
<lb n="0028a13" ed="T"/>民所居莊<note n="0028004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">室＝宅【甲】</note><app n="0028004"><lem wit="【大】">室</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">宅</rdg></app>房舍。<note n="0028005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">皆＋（於）【甲】</note><app n="0028005"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">皆於</rdg></app>於中心取少分處安
<lb n="0028a14" ed="T"/>置此像。其八方鎮處即作四臂大<note n="0028006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔嚴〕－【甲】</note><app n="0028006"><lem wit="【大】">嚴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>忿怒身。
<lb n="0028a15" ed="T"/>紺青色洪滿端嚴。目口皆張利牙上出。右劍
<lb n="0028a16" ed="T"/>左索。其上二臂在口兩邊作忿怒印。身處八
<lb n="0028a17" ed="T"/>幅金剛輪。內其輪。四外現八三股金剛杵頭。
<lb n="0028a18" ed="T"/><note n="0028007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">輪＝輻【甲】</note><app n="0028007"><lem wit="【大】">輪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">輻</rdg></app>復有<app source="0028003" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">伽</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">迦</rdg></app>樓羅炎。坐<note n="0028008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">四大＝大四【甲】</note><app n="0028008"><lem wit="【大】">四大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">大四</rdg></app>寶須彌山上。及
<lb n="0028a19" ed="T"/>八<note n="0028009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">天＋（王）【甲】</note><app n="0028009"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">天王</rdg></app>并諸眷屬。及鑄金輪自有圖樣。上從王
<lb n="0028a20" ed="T"/>宮下至黎庶悉行此法。若不遍行無有是處。
<lb n="0028a21" ed="T"/>皆於所居安置形像勿生怖畏。我本先願不
<lb n="0028a22" ed="T"/>捨眾生。常居一處渾同穢濁悉令清淨。及施
<lb n="0028a23" ed="T"/>殘食而為供養。并受大日如來五字心真言。
<lb n="0028a24" ed="T"/>并軍旅眾生亦帶此<note n="0028010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔悉〕－【甲】，悉＝心&M062485;【原】</note><app n="0028010"><lem wit="【大】"><sic resp="【原】" corr="心">悉</sic></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0028011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">真言＝受真言誦&M062303;【原】</note><app n="0028011"><lem wit="【大】">真言</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ｂ】">受真言誦</rdg></app>及施殘食。令
<lb n="0028a25" ed="T"/>增勝福。其王宮中每月一日及十五日依法
<lb n="0028a26" ed="T"/>供養。以諸香華上<note n="0028012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">妙＋（幢蓋繒）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0028012"><lem wit="【大】">妙</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">妙幢蓋繒</rdg></app><note n="0028013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">幡＋（蓋山）【甲】</note><app n="0028013"><lem wit="【大】">幡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">幡蓋山</rdg></app>寶網。蘇燈閼伽寶
<lb n="0028a27" ed="T"/>瓶寶器微妙塗香。<note n="0028014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（種種）＋上【甲】</note><app n="0028014"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">種種上</rdg></app>味珍妙甘&CB00498;及諸湯藥。
<lb n="0028a28" ed="T"/>并陳種種上妙音樂。其王爾時捨憍慢心生
<lb n="0028a29" ed="T"/>謙下心。普為國界及諸人民親自祈哀。恭敬
<pb n="0028b" id="T21.1203.0028b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0028b01" ed="T"/>供養<note n="0028015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">施＝旋&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0028015"><lem wit="【大】">施</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">旋</rdg></app>繞禮拜。殷勤祈請發殊勝願。增加福
<lb n="0028b02" ed="T"/>力人民安樂不受諸難。每年春秋依教戶摩。
<lb n="0028b03" ed="T"/>如法供養表王志重。於諸有情不生疲倦。為
<lb n="0028b04" ed="T"/>我國界求勝上福。如是陳設八鎮之後。其國
<lb n="0028b05" ed="T"/>永斷一切災禍。天龍歡喜愍念眾生。諸佛常
<lb n="0028b06" ed="T"/><note n="0028016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔當〕－【甲】</note><app n="0028016"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>護念一切有情。為加持故俱修慚愧共行
<lb n="0028b07" ed="T"/>十善。國界自然安穩豐饒。其諸人民受諸快
<lb n="0028b08" ed="T"/>樂。仁王所化倍增福德相繼不絕。壽命增
<lb n="0028b09" ed="T"/>長國土榮盛。有<note n="0028017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔大〕－【甲】</note><app n="0028017"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>威力如師子王無能勝者。
<lb n="0028b10" ed="T"/>爾時世尊以偈讚曰。</p>
<lb n="0028b11" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT21p0028b1101"><l>我大日如來</l><l>安鎮家國法</l>
<lb n="0028b12" ed="T"/><l>現威德自在</l><l>號不動明王</l>
<lb n="0028b13" ed="T"/><l>於一切有情</l><l>斷三惡道業</l>
<lb n="0028b14" ed="T"/><l>能離諸八難</l><l>使三界獲安</l>
<lb n="0028b15" ed="T"/><l>故贊說修行</l><l>及戶摩儀軌</l>
<lb n="0028b16" ed="T"/><l>供養當時分</l><l>宿曜日相應</l>
<lb n="0028b17" ed="T"/><l>一一悉加持</l><l>清淨無雜染</l>
<lb n="0028b18" ed="T"/><l>住三密觀行</l><l>所作<note n="0028018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">俱＝具&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0028018"><lem wit="【大】">俱</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">具</rdg></app>威儀</l>
<lb n="0028b19" ed="T"/><l>三日午前起</l><l>五日午後成</l>
<lb n="0028b20" ed="T"/><l>中夜後戶摩</l><l>大陽安鎮畢</l>
<lb n="0028b21" ed="T"/><l>大悲根本號</l><l>五字心真言</l>
<lb n="0028b22" ed="T"/><l>王&CB00330;普流行</l><l>軍眾皆帶受</l>
<lb n="0028b23" ed="T"/><l>建立尊形像</l><l>印契具分明</l>
<lb n="0028b24" ed="T"/><l>童子威怒身</l><l>面貌皆充滿</l>
<lb n="0028b25" ed="T"/><l>儀軌及供養</l><l>教令悉相應</l>
<lb n="0028b26" ed="T"/><l>曼<note n="0028019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拏＝荼&M062403;【原】＊</note><app n="0028019"><lem wit="【大】">拏</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">荼</rdg></app>羅普通</l><l>根本自差別</l>
<lb n="0028b27" ed="T"/><l>如上次第法</l><l>每鎮畫像前</l>
<lb n="0028b28" ed="T"/><l>起從憍尸迦</l><l>右旋伊舍畢</l>
<lb n="0028b29" ed="T"/><l>周百由旬內</l><l>四臂大怒王</l>
<pb n="0028c" id="T21.1203.0028c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0028c01" ed="T"/><l>一髻左下垂</l><l>身作紺青色</l>
<lb n="0028c02" ed="T"/><l>半跏彌盧上</l><l>成就斫羯羅</l>
<lb n="0028c03" ed="T"/><l>猛焰從心生</l><l>狀如金翅鳥</l>
<lb n="0028c04" ed="T"/><l>八天依本位</l><l>面向聖尊前</l>
<lb n="0028c05" ed="T"/><l>持自契真言</l><l>眷屬皆奉獻</l>
<lb n="0028c06" ed="T"/><l>龍神咸歡喜</l><l>稱美讚<note n="0028020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">人＝仁&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0028020" resp="【原】" corr="仁">人</sic>王</l>
<lb n="0028c07" ed="T"/><l>八難不能侵</l><l>一切同安樂</l>
<lb n="0028c08" ed="T"/><l>所有難調者</l><l>災變自消除</l>
<lb n="0028c09" ed="T"/><l>設使軍陳中</l><l>斷彼人身命</l>
<lb n="0028c10" ed="T"/><l>為帶真言故</l><l>大士力加持</l>
<lb n="0028c11" ed="T"/><l>永絕怨害因</l><l>生勝不動國</l>
<lb n="0028c12" ed="T"/><l>其王安近處</l><l>兩臂根本身</l>
<lb n="0028c13" ed="T"/><l>黃色坐金山</l><l>作俱摩羅相</l>
<lb n="0028c14" ed="T"/><l>以幡華<note n="0028021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">縵＝鬘&M062403;【原】，繒【甲】</note><note n="0028021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">縵＝鬘&M062403;【原】，＝繒【甲】</note><app n="0028021"><lem wit="【大】">縵</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">鬘</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">繒</rdg></app>蓋</l><l>種種妙莊嚴</l>
<lb n="0028c15" ed="T"/><l>初<note n="0028022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">月＝日&M062303;【原】，白【甲】</note><note n="0028022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">月＝日&M062303;【原】，＝白【甲】</note><app n="0028022"><lem wit="【大】">月</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ｂ】">日</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">白</rdg></app>十五晨</l><l>王親自瞻仰</l>
<lb n="0028c16" ed="T"/><l>所捨於殘食</l><l>奉獻不動尊</l>
<lb n="0028c17" ed="T"/><l>供養勿生疑</l><l>成真實上味</l>
<lb n="0028c18" ed="T"/><l>迴奉十方佛</l><l>我願滿眾生</l>
<lb n="0028c19" ed="T"/><l>大千國土中</l><l>一切同安樂</l></lg>
<lb n="0028c20" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0028c2001">次說<note n="0028023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">隨＋（方）【甲】</note><app n="0028023"><lem wit="【大】">隨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">隨方</rdg></app>安鎮法。當欲鎮時。先起東方。<note n="0028024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔東方〕－【甲】</note><app n="0028024"><lem wit="【大】">東方</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0028c21" ed="T"/>擇勝上地。無諸穢惡結界加持。當其鎮處
<lb n="0028c22" ed="T"/>掘深三肘廣亦三肘。以瞿<note n="0028025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩＋（夷）【甲】</note><app n="0028025"><lem wit="【大】">摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">摩夷</rdg></app>塗飾。辦備塗
<lb n="0028c23" ed="T"/>香閼伽燈明飲食蘇乳&CB00031;子。別作一<note n="0028026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（一）＋肘【甲】</note><app n="0028026"><lem wit="【大】">肘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">一肘</rdg></app>方曼
<lb n="0028c24" ed="T"/><app source="0028019" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">拏</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">荼</rdg></app>羅。於此壇上置本尊像。幡華嚴飾廣設供
<lb n="0028c25" ed="T"/>養。當於中夜作戶摩業。其<note n="0028027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">所＋（鎮）【甲】</note><app n="0028027"><lem wit="【大】">所</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">所鎮</rdg></app>處以金銀&CB00222;璃
<lb n="0028c26" ed="T"/>珊瑚馬瑙真珠琥珀及以七寶布輪上。於輪
<lb n="0028c27" ed="T"/>齊中下鑌鐵橛加持一千八十遍。一遍<note n="0028028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一下＝下一【甲】</note><app n="0028028"><lem wit="【大】">一下</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">下一</rdg></app>
<lb n="0028c28" ed="T"/>槌乃至遍數畢。四角散五穀。即下土填平。欲
<lb n="0028c29" ed="T"/>鎮之時。從午後至夜半前候取吉祥時分。即
<pb n="0029a" id="T21.1203.0029a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0029a01" ed="T"/>當下鎮了後夜戶摩。其壇四傍。依五方色。繒
<lb n="0029a02" ed="T"/>綵錢帛鎮之。取明相分修功德了。於其鎮處
<lb n="0029a03" ed="T"/>其上置一素不動明王四臂者。及本方天眷
<lb n="0029a04" ed="T"/>屬。各執本契香華向尊供養。其素像取囉惹
<lb n="0029a05" ed="T"/>身量長短為之。其功<note n="0029001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">未＝已&M062303;【原】</note><app n="0029001"><lem wit="【大】">未</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ｂ】">已</rdg></app>畢。且開眼目。廣大
<lb n="0029a06" ed="T"/>供養設大<note n="0029002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">音＝意【甲】</note><app n="0029002"><lem wit="【大】">音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">意</rdg></app>樂。悉令殊勝依此鎮已。如是周
<lb n="0029a07" ed="T"/>遍八方。並如上<note n="0029003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">說＝訖【甲】</note><app n="0029003"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">訖</rdg></app>。即<note n="0029004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（於）＋王【甲】</note><app n="0029004"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">於王</rdg></app>宮置兩臂根本不
<lb n="0029a08" ed="T"/>動明王。依法建立如教安置已。即&CB00330;下四方
<lb n="0029a09" ed="T"/>王<note n="0029005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">令＝命【甲】</note><app n="0029005"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">命</rdg></app>及處。上從宰相百官下至黎庶所居室
<lb n="0029a10" ed="T"/>內。如前安立不<note n="0029006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">動＋（明王）【甲】</note><app n="0029006"><lem wit="【大】">動</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">動明王</rdg></app>像。及令誦五字心真言并
<lb n="0029a11" ed="T"/>行。當制嚴令彌加<note n="0029007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">戒＝誡&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0029007"><lem wit="【大】">戒</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">誡</rdg></app>勸。殘食供養勿令斷絕。
<lb n="0029a12" ed="T"/>共持國界安<note n="0029008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鎮＝樂【甲】</note><app n="0029008"><lem wit="【大】">鎮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">樂</rdg></app>普同。設有於此大聖尊前。歌
<lb n="0029a13" ed="T"/>舞戲笑生輕慢心。此大明王亦不生厭離。我
<lb n="0029a14" ed="T"/>施勝福。若諸有情施少殘食供養我者。即同
<lb n="0029a15" ed="T"/>以十方無量勝妙珍玩。百味飲食衣服臥具。
<lb n="0029a16" ed="T"/>上妙湯藥七寶宮殿。象馬車乘僮僕。奉施功
<lb n="0029a17" ed="T"/>德無異。復過於此百千萬倍。即成真實廣大
<lb n="0029a18" ed="T"/>供養。修供養時最相應者。<note n="0029009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（&CB00473;）＋赤【甲】</note><app n="0029009"><lem wit="【大】">赤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB00473;赤</rdg></app>色衣服皆大吉
<lb n="0029a19" ed="T"/>祥。次說作戶摩鑪及所用物。若戶摩時。於
<lb n="0029a20" ed="T"/>明王前作戶摩鑪廣一肘深半肘。取本處城
<lb n="0029a21" ed="T"/>邑四邊順流水及彼河<note n="0029010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩＝岸【甲】</note><app n="0029010"><lem wit="【大】">摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">岸</rdg></app>土。及雜香加持和
<lb n="0029a22" ed="T"/><note n="0029011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以＝為【甲】</note><app n="0029011"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">為</rdg></app>泥。以用泥鑪壇。復以瞿摩塗拭。中心劍
<lb n="0029a23" ed="T"/>契。行者左邊囉惹位。次大臣位。次大將位。次
<lb n="0029a24" ed="T"/>地主<note n="0029012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">位＋（此地主）【甲】</note><app n="0029012"><lem wit="【大】">位</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">位此地主</rdg></app>。應須親入道場發至誠心。<note n="0029013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">本＝大【甲】</note><app n="0029013"><lem wit="【大】">本</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">大</rdg></app>位中
<lb n="0029a25" ed="T"/>坐道場內不得過三人。於壇外四面七步外。
<lb n="0029a26" ed="T"/>嚴整甲兵執持器仗一如法。及奏種種上妙
<lb n="0029a27" ed="T"/>伎樂。大陳供養廣宣王命。於大聖尊前為一
<lb n="0029a28" ed="T"/>切有情。如法安<note n="0029014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔立〕－【甲】</note><app n="0029014"><lem wit="【大】">立</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>本方天像并諸眷屬。修功
<lb n="0029a29" ed="T"/>德時當<note n="0029015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">見＝占【甲】</note><app n="0029015"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">占</rdg></app>火相。如有不祥依教攘之。既安鎮
<pb n="0029b" id="T21.1203.0029b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0029b01" ed="T"/>了。即於當處召取三人能修行者令彼受持。
<lb n="0029b02" ed="T"/>三時焚香灑掃供養。每月一日及十五日。燈
<lb n="0029b03" ed="T"/>明飲食種種音樂如法供養。諸天歡喜護持
<lb n="0029b04" ed="T"/>此界。無有衰難一<note n="0029016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">切安＝安切【甲】</note><app n="0029016"><lem wit="【大】">切安</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">安切</rdg></app>樂。其戶摩時。用牛蘇
<lb n="0029b05" ed="T"/>四斤<note n="0029017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">或＋（用）【甲】</note><app n="0029017"><lem wit="【大】">或</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">或用</rdg></app>二斤。五穀巨勝乳酪飲食。&CB00031;子蠟燭
<lb n="0029b06" ed="T"/>菉豆子。塗香五味<note n="0029018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">沈香＝香沈【甲】</note><app n="0029018"><lem wit="【大】">沈香</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">香沈</rdg></app>檀蘇合。龍腦&CB00614;金安
<lb n="0029b07" ed="T"/>悉乳頭白芥子蜜。隨施主年記。乳木長十二
<lb n="0029b08" ed="T"/>指。菉豆白<note n="0029019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">膠＋（草白豆）【甲】</note><app n="0029019"><lem wit="【大】">膠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">膠草白豆</rdg></app>&CB04287;子及羅惹上服以<note n="0029020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">代＝伐【甲】</note><app n="0029020"><lem wit="【大】">代</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">伐</rdg></app>其位。
<lb n="0029b09" ed="T"/>如同道場將用所表。如親自供養瞻仰無異。
<lb n="0029b10" ed="T"/>每鎮鑌鐵橛銅輪。各一橛長八指一半已上。
<lb n="0029b11" ed="T"/>作獨股形仍具<note n="0029021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（八）＋楞【甲】</note><app n="0029021"><lem wit="【大】">楞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">八楞</rdg></app>。已下橛形可入輪齊。四指
<lb n="0029b12" ed="T"/>輪廣一肘。內八輻外八方各出三股半金剛杵
<lb n="0029b13" ed="T"/>頭。輪齊有孔可容鑌橛金銅。戶摩杓二。每鎮
<lb n="0029b14" ed="T"/>不動尊旗一口。本方天王旗一口。軍馬行時。
<lb n="0029b15" ed="T"/>即將引前。大將隨後。若不行時。於本像處安
<lb n="0029b16" ed="T"/>置勿令穢污。<note n="0029022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">若＝其【甲】</note><app n="0029022"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">其</rdg></app>戶摩時。若初若末皆投蘇三
<lb n="0029b17" ed="T"/>杓。審看其相。若土地人民。役災變善惡有不
<lb n="0029b18" ed="T"/>祥相。依教攘之。如有惡相。不作<note n="0029023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">功＋（德）【甲】</note><app n="0029023"><lem wit="【大】">功</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">功德</rdg></app>。三年之
<lb n="0029b19" ed="T"/>內必有應驗。不然別作大福。隨處迴援即須
<lb n="0029b20" ed="T"/>為之。若戶摩時。<note n="0029024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">火＝大【甲】</note><app n="0029024"><lem wit="【大】">火</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">大</rdg></app>相右旋<note n="0029025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">光＋（明）【甲】</note><app n="0029025"><lem wit="【大】">光</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">光明</rdg></app>焰直上。或作
<lb n="0029b21" ed="T"/>音樂鐘鈴妙聲。及形像者為大善相。若復左
<lb n="0029b22" ed="T"/><note n="0029026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">施＝旋【甲】</note><app n="0029026"><lem wit="【大】">施</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">旋</rdg></app>作不祥鳥獸形。又作呵呵之聲。於其土地
<lb n="0029b23" ed="T"/><note n="0029027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">亦＝必【甲】＊</note><app n="0029027"><lem wit="【大】">亦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">必</rdg></app>有災難。眾生飢凍水旱不時人民<note n="0029028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">飢＝餓【甲】</note><app n="0029028"><lem wit="【大】">飢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">餓</rdg></app>死。
<lb n="0029b24" ed="T"/>應作息災法攘<note n="0029029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">之＋（若火星迸散雷霹之聲必有兵甲流散不相順伏作增益法攘之）【甲】</note><app n="0029029"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">之若火星迸散雷霹之聲必有兵甲流散不相順伏作增益法攘之</rdg></app>。若戶摩時。火成雲霧黑闇
<lb n="0029b25" ed="T"/>向下垂布。鑪中火滅供養不成者。其地<app source="0029027" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">亦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">必</rdg></app>有
<lb n="0029b26" ed="T"/>隱相謀害。作調伏法攘之。已上四種善惡之
<lb n="0029b27" ed="T"/>相<note n="0029030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">極＋（須）【甲】</note><app n="0029030"><lem wit="【大】">極</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">極須</rdg></app>用意。審細詳察隨相攘之。若息災時用
<lb n="0029b28" ed="T"/>乳木。鑪中輪印。<note n="0029031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">句食＝白食衣【甲】</note><app n="0029031"><lem wit="【大】">句食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">白食衣</rdg></app>衣白衣。若增益時用
<lb n="0029b29" ed="T"/>白<note n="0029032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">壇＝檀&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0029032"><lem wit="【大】">壇</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">檀</rdg></app>木。鑪中幢印。衣食俱赤。若敬愛時用
<pb n="0029c" id="T21.1203.0029c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0029c01" ed="T"/>蓮華投火。如無雜華代之。鑪中蓮華印。衣食
<lb n="0029c02" ed="T"/>俱紅色。若調伏時投苦練木棘針皂莢刺及
<lb n="0029c03" ed="T"/>毒藥等。衣食皆<note n="0029033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">黑＝青【甲】</note><app n="0029033"><lem wit="【大】">黑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">青</rdg></app>。若金輪王為四天下有情
<lb n="0029c04" ed="T"/>安鎮者。可<note n="0029034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">周＝用&M062303;【原】</note><app n="0029034"><lem wit="【大】">周</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ｂ】">用</rdg></app>一萬由旬內鎮。若銀輪王<note n="0029035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔為〕－【甲】</note><app n="0029035"><lem wit="【大】">為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0029c05" ed="T"/>八千由旬內鎮。若銅輪王六<note n="0029036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">十＝千【甲】</note><app n="0029036"><lem wit="【大】">十</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">千</rdg></app>由旬內鎮。若
<lb n="0029c06" ed="T"/>鐵輪王三千由旬內鎮。<note n="0029037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（若）＋為【甲】</note><app n="0029037"><lem wit="【大】">為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">若為</rdg></app>當國眾生周百由
<lb n="0029c07" ed="T"/>旬內鎮之。於王城每方面一千里內。<note n="0029038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">王＋（城）&M062485;【原】，王＝五【甲】</note><app n="0029038"><lem wit="【大】"><sic resp="【原】" corr="王城">王</sic></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">五</rdg></app>百里
<lb n="0029c08" ed="T"/>外當取所便處安鎮。但不過其位。即得如是。
<lb n="0029c09" ed="T"/>安鎮儀式及曼<app source="0028019" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">拏</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">荼</rdg></app>羅并其形像。所用諸物皆
<lb n="0029c10" ed="T"/>已略說。汝諸有情發菩提心。為一切有情。依
<lb n="0029c11" ed="T"/>教修學戶摩鑪<note n="0029039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">樣＝橛【甲】</note><app n="0029039"><lem wit="【大】">樣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">橛</rdg></app>及布列<note n="0029040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">像＝儀軌&M062303;【原】，儀【甲】</note><note n="0029040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">像＝儀軌&M062303;【原】，＝儀【甲】</note><app n="0029040"><lem wit="【大】">像</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ｂ】">儀軌</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">儀</rdg></app>。若調伏時不應
<lb n="0029c12" ed="T"/>顯名目作。必須祕密為之。勿使當處知。唯監
<lb n="0029c13" ed="T"/>者知之。藥物先須備擬。自將行要即用之。</p></div1>
<lb n="0029c14" ed="T"/><div1 type="W"><p id="pT21p0029c1401">如此祕法不許出家人行。持此法者。所作
<lb n="0029c15" ed="T"/>供養皆須自禮拜諸天。出<note n="0029041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">家＋（之）【甲】</note><app n="0029041"><lem wit="【大】">家</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">家之</rdg></app>人具佛禁戒。
<lb n="0029c16" ed="T"/>令諸<note n="0029042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">人＝天【甲】</note><app n="0029042"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">天</rdg></app>不安不敢受<note n="0029043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拜＝禮【甲】</note><app n="0029043"><lem wit="【大】">拜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">禮</rdg></app>。所求福德悉不
<lb n="0029c17" ed="T"/>成就故。違行者當犯大罪。是以<note n="0029044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不＋（得）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0029044"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">不得</rdg></app>傳出家
<lb n="0029c18" ed="T"/>之人。本法金剛智三藏。於天竺大師所受
<lb n="0029c19" ed="T"/>得。勿令傳之。只許授與白衣。修行者祕之
<lb n="0029c20" ed="T"/>祕之。西方深重此法。設欲行<note n="0029045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">密之＝祕密行之&M062403;【原】，之密&M062303;【原】，密行之【甲】</note><note n="0029045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">密之＝祕密行之&M062403;【原】，＝之密&M062303;【原】，＝密行之【甲】</note><app n="0029045"><lem wit="【大】">密之</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">祕密行之</rdg><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ｂ】">之密</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">密行之</rdg></app>不令諸
<lb n="0029c21" ed="T"/>國知有。是以西國相承繼嗣不絕。又西方
<lb n="0029c22" ed="T"/>慳法只流<note n="0029046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尊＋（身）【甲】</note><app n="0029046"><lem wit="【大】">尊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">尊身</rdg></app>樣。於諸部中以為大護。殊不
<lb n="0029c23" ed="T"/>知有安鎮家國等法。金剛智三藏<note n="0029047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">受＝授&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0029047"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">授</rdg></app>與行
<lb n="0029c24" ed="T"/>者王<note n="0029048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">光＝先【甲】</note><app n="0029048"><lem wit="【大】">光</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">先</rdg></app>此儀軌法。</p></div1>
<pb n="0030a" id="T21.1203.0030a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030a01" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT21p0030a0101">不動尊摧他敵八方天王旗幡并八方天降怨
<lb n="0030a02" ed="T"/>真言法</p>
<lb n="0030a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030a0301">東方作白色旗。旗上畫帝釋天王。右手持獨
<lb n="0030a04" ed="T"/>股杵。左手叉腰。乘六牙白象。持白旗人誦天
<lb n="0030a05" ed="T"/>帝釋降怨真言。明曰。</p>
<lb n="0030a06" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030a0601" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd"><note n="0030001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔&SD-CFC8;〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0030001"><lem wit="【大】">&SD-CFC8;</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">&lac;</rdg></app></t><t lang="chi"><note n="0030002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">因＝印【甲】</note><app n="0030002"><lem wit="【大】">因</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">印</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E04B;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>捺羅</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0030003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">野泥＝夜提【甲】</note>野</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A56F;</t><t lang="chi">泥</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00085;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A57D;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0030004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">地婆多＝底婆哆【甲】</note>地</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi">婆</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi">曳</t></tt>
<lb n="0030a07" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030a08" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC1;</t><t lang="chi">吽</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5C1;</t><t lang="chi">發</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E046;</t><t lang="chi">吒</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi">賀</t></tt></p>
<lb n="0030a09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030a10" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030a1001">若東行時。先引此旗。想天帝釋領無量眷屬
<lb n="0030a11" ed="T"/>天眾。持種種器仗衝彼賊眾。</p>
<lb n="0030a12" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030a1201">東南方作黃色旗。旗上畫四臂火天。乘<note n="0030005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">青＝白【甲】</note><app n="0030005"><lem wit="【大】">青</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">白</rdg></app>羊
<lb n="0030a13" ed="T"/>遍身火焰。右手作<note n="0030006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">施＋（願）【甲】</note><app n="0030006"><lem wit="【大】">施</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">施願</rdg></app>無畏。第二持念珠。左
<lb n="0030a14" ed="T"/>手持仙杖。第二持澡瓶。持<note n="0030007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（黃）&M062403;＋旗【原】</note><app n="0030007"><lem wit="【大】">旗</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">黃旗</rdg></app>人誦火天降怨
<lb n="0030a15" ed="T"/>真言。明曰。</p>
<lb n="0030a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030a1601" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC5;</t><t lang="chi">阿</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B349;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>&CB00344;曩</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi">曳</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B7BE;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><note n="0030008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00069;旨二合＝哩只二合【甲】</note><note n="0030008" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>&CB00069;旨二合＝哩只二合【甲】</note><zi>&CB00069;旨</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC5;</t><t lang="chi">阿</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A57D;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0030009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">地頗多＝底婆哆【甲】</note>地</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi">頗</t></tt>
<lb n="0030a17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030a18" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi">曳</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC1;</t><t lang="chi">吽</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5C1;</t><t lang="chi">發</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E046;</t><t lang="chi">吒</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi">賀</t></tt></p>
<lb n="0030a19" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030a20" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030a2001">若東南行時。先引此旗。想火天領無量<note n="0030010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">火＋（天）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0030010"><lem wit="【大】">火</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">火天</rdg></app>仙
<lb n="0030a21" ed="T"/>軍持種種器仗衝彼賊眾。</p>
<lb n="0030a22" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030a2201">南方作黑色旗。旗上畫焰摩羅天。乘水牛。右
<lb n="0030a23" ed="T"/>手持焰摩幢。左手叉腰。持<note n="0030011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（黑）&M062403;＋旗【原】</note><app n="0030011"><lem wit="【大】">旗</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">黑旗</rdg></app>人誦焰摩王降
<lb n="0030a24" ed="T"/>怨真言。明曰。</p>
<lb n="0030a25" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030a2501" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FB;</t><t lang="chi">閻</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E6;</t><t lang="chi">摩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0030012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">野波&CB03947;三合＝夜比&CB14670;【甲】</note><note n="0030012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">野波<app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">&CB01418;</lem><rdg wit="【大】">&CB03947;</rdg></app>三合＝夜比&CB14670;【甲】</note>野</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-AABC;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>波&CB01418;</zi><sg><note n="0030013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＝二&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0030013"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">二</rdg></app>合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A558;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A57D;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0030014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">地頗多＝底波哆【甲】</note>地</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi">頗</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt>
<lb n="0030a26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030a27" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi">曳</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC1;</t><t lang="chi">吽</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5C1;</t><t lang="chi">發</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E046;</t><t lang="chi">吒</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi">賀</t></tt></p>
<lb n="0030a28" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030a29" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030a2901">若<note n="0030015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">南＋（方）【甲】</note><app n="0030015"><lem wit="【大】">南</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">南方</rdg></app>行時。先引此旗。想炎摩王領無量鬼
<pb n="0030b" id="T21.1203.0030b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030b01" ed="T"/>軍。持種種器仗衝彼賊眾。</p>
<lb n="0030b02" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030b0201">西南方作<note n="0030016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慘＝燥&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0030016" resp="【原】" corr="燥">慘</sic>色旗。旗上畫羅剎主。乘師子。
<lb n="0030b03" ed="T"/>右手持<note n="0030017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（煙）&M062403;＋劍【原】</note><app n="0030017"><lem wit="【大】">劍</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">煙劍</rdg></app>。左手叉腰。持<note n="0030018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（煙）&M062403;＋旗【原】</note><app n="0030018"><lem wit="【大】">旗</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">煙旗</rdg></app>人誦羅剎主降
<lb n="0030b04" ed="T"/>怨真言。明曰。</p>
<lb n="0030b05" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030b0501" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A559;</t><t lang="chi">底</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A640;</t><t lang="chi">哩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B770;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>地曳</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">羅</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6B4;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>乞<note n="0030019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">剎＝叉&M062403;【原】，剎二合沙地頗多＝叉娑底波吒【甲】</note>剎</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67B;</t><t lang="chi">沙</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A57D;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0030020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">地頗＝底婆&M062403;【原】</note>地</t></tt>
<lb n="0030b06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030b07" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi">頗</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi">曳</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC1;</t><t lang="chi">吽</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5C1;</t><t lang="chi">發</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E046;</t><t lang="chi">吒</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi">賀</t></tt></p>
<lb n="0030b08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030b09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030b0901">若西南行時。先引此旗。想羅剎主領無量羅
<lb n="0030b10" ed="T"/>剎。持種種器仗衝彼賊眾。</p>
<lb n="0030b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030b1101">西方作赤色旗。旗上畫水天。乘龜。<note n="0030021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">右＋（手）【甲】</note><app n="0030021"><lem wit="【大】">右</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">右手</rdg></app>執蛇
<lb n="0030b12" ed="T"/>索。左手叉腰。其天頭上有七龍頭狀如蛇形。
<lb n="0030b13" ed="T"/>持<note n="0030022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（赤）&M062403;＋旗【原】</note><app n="0030022"><lem wit="【大】">旗</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">赤旗</rdg></app>人誦水天降怨真言。明曰。</p>
<lb n="0030b14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030b1401" type="dharani">
<tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt>
<tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00085;</t></tt>
<tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A642;</t><t lang="chi">嚕</t></tt>
<tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A54B;</t><t lang="chi">拏</t></tt>
<tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0030023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">野曩&CB00344;地頗多＝夜那伽底婆多&M062403;【原】，夜那&CB00344;底波哆【甲】</note>野</t></tt>
<tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt>
<tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A459;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00344;</t></tt>
<tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A57D;</t><t lang="chi">地</t></tt>
<tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi">頗</t></tt>
<tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt>
<tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi">曳</t></tt>
<tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC1;</t><t lang="chi">吽</t></tt>
<lb n="0030b15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030b16" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5C1;</t><t lang="chi">發</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E046;</t><t lang="chi">吒</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi">賀</t></tt></p>
<lb n="0030b17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030b1801">若西行時。先引此旗。想水天領無量毒龍。持
<lb n="0030b19" ed="T"/>種種器仗衝彼賊眾。</p>
<lb n="0030b20" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030b2001">西北方作青色旗。旗上畫風天。乘&CB00538;。右手持
<lb n="0030b21" ed="T"/>旗。左手叉腰。持<note n="0030024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（青）&M062403;＋旗【原】</note><app n="0030024"><lem wit="【大】">旗</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">青旗</rdg></app>人誦風天降怨真言。明
<lb n="0030b22" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
<lb n="0030b23" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030b2301" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A657;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00085;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0030025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">野＝夜&M062403;【原】，野吠佉左嚕地頗多＝夜吠捨車羅底波哆【甲】</note>野</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A65C;</t><t lang="chi">吠</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A44C;</t><t lang="chi">佉</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A47C;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0030026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">左嚕地頗＝車羅底婆&M062403;【原】</note>左</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FE;</t><t lang="chi">嚕</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A57D;</t><t lang="chi">地</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi">頗</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi">曳</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC1;</t><t lang="chi">吽</t></tt>
<lb n="0030b24" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030b25" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5C1;</t><t lang="chi">發</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E046;</t><t lang="chi">吒</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi">賀</t></tt></p>
<lb n="0030b26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030b27" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030b2701">若<note n="0030027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">西＋（北）&M062403;【原】，西方＝西北【甲】</note><note n="0030027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">西方＝西北【甲】，西＋（北）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0030027"><lem wit="【大】">西方</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">西北</rdg><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">西北方</rdg></app>行時。先引此旗。想風天領無量金翅
<lb n="0030b28" ed="T"/>鳥王。持種種器仗衝彼賊眾。</p>
<lb n="0030b29" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030b2901">北方作黃色旗。旗上畫毘沙門天王。乘鬼。右
<pb n="0030c" id="T21.1203.0030c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030c01" ed="T"/>手持<note n="0030028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">寶塔＝花棒【甲】</note><app n="0030028"><lem wit="【大】">寶塔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">花棒</rdg></app>。左手叉腰。持旗人誦毘沙門天王
<lb n="0030c02" ed="T"/>降怨真言。明曰。</p>
<lb n="0030c03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030c0301" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A444;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0030029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">俱吠囉＝矩伏羅【甲】</note>俱</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A65D;</t><t lang="chi">吠</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">囉</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;</t><t lang="chi">夜</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6B5;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>乞叉</zi><sg><note n="0030030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合〕－【甲】</note><app n="0030030"><lem wit="【大】">二合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A57D;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0030031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">地頗多＝底婆多&M062403;【原】＊，底波多【甲】＊</note><note n="0030031" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>地頗多＝底婆多&M062403;【原】＊，底波多【甲】＊</note>地</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi">頗</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt>
<lb n="0030c04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030c05" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi">曳</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC1;</t><t lang="chi">吽</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5C1;</t><t lang="chi">發</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E046;</t><t lang="chi">吒</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi">賀</t></tt></p>
<lb n="0030c06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030c07" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030c0701">若<note n="0030032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">北＋（方）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0030032"><lem wit="【大】">北</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ａ】">北方</rdg></app>行時。先引此旗。想毘沙門天王領無量
<lb n="0030c08" ed="T"/>藥叉軍眾。持種種器仗衝彼賊眾。</p>
<lb n="0030c09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030c0901">東北方作<note n="0030033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">線＝綠【甲】</note><app n="0030033"><lem wit="【大】">線</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">綠</rdg></app>色旗。<note n="0030034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（旗）＋上【甲】</note><app n="0030034"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">旗上</rdg></app>畫伊舍那天。乘&CB01738;牛。
<lb n="0030c10" ed="T"/>右手持三股叉。在手叉腰。持旗人誦伊舍那
<lb n="0030c11" ed="T"/>天降怨真言。明曰。</p>
<lb n="0030c12" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030c1201" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA42;</t><t lang="chi">唵</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC8;</t><t lang="chi">伊</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A663;</t><t lang="chi">舍</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0030035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">那野步多＝曩夜捺囉吒【甲】</note>那</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;</t><t lang="chi">野</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5DD;</t><t lang="chi">步</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A558;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A57D;</t><t lang="chi"><anchor id="fxT21p0030c01"/>地</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi">頗</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F7;</t><t lang="chi">曳</t></tt>
<lb n="0030c13" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030c14" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA74;</t>
<t lang="chi">吽</t>
</tt>
<tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5C1;</t><t lang="chi">發</t></tt>
<tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E046;</t><t lang="chi">吒</t></tt>
<tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-B065;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>娑&CB00085;</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt>
<tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi">賀</t></tt>
</p>
<lb n="0030c15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030c16" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030c1601">若東北方行時。先引此旗。想伊舍那天領無
<lb n="0030c17" ed="T"/>量鬼軍將士。持種種器仗衝彼賊眾。</p>
<lb n="0030c18" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030c1801">大將自誦不動尊明王真言。想自身成不動
<lb n="0030c19" ed="T"/>明王。又想不動尊明王號令八方天王云。
<lb n="0030c20" ed="T"/>汝等各領無量軍眾摧彼逆賊。其大將不
<lb n="0030c21" ed="T"/>斷絕。誦不動尊明王真言。若作此法。彼賊
<lb n="0030c22" ed="T"/>自當殄滅決定無疑。即說聖不動明王真言。
<lb n="0030c23" ed="T"/><note n="0030036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔明〕－【甲】</note><app n="0030036"><lem wit="【大】">明</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>曰。</p>
<lb n="0030c24" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0030c2401" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F0;</t><t lang="chi">莫</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">三</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E5;</t><t lang="chi">滿</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CA56;</t><t lang="chi">多</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A656;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00085;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A9BD;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>日囉</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A555;</t><t lang="chi">&CB00718;</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A47C;</t><t lang="chi">戰</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-C9FD;</t><t lang="chi">荼</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E5;</t><t lang="chi">摩</t></tt>
<lb n="0030c25" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030c26" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi">訶</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A646;</t><t lang="chi">嚕</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A66E;</t><t lang="chi">灑</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A54B;</t><t lang="chi">拏<note place="inline">發願某甲軍眾摧彼逆賊。願彼逆賊大敗。仍稱逆人名</note></t></tt>
<lb n="0030c27" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030c28" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CDF1;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>沙頗</zi><sg>二合</sg></yin></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E046;</t><t lang="chi">吒</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F1;</t><t lang="chi">野</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC1;</t><t lang="chi">吽</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-AA5E;</t><t lang="chi">怛囉</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E046;</t><t lang="chi">吒</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E1A2;</t><t lang="chi">憾&CB00805;</t></tt></p>
<lb n="0030c29" ed="T"/>
<pb n="0031a" id="T21.1203.0031a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0031a01" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0031a0101">若行營所八旗在外。各依本方圍諸軍將士
<lb n="0031a02" ed="T"/>卒所下營<note n="0031001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">止＝上【甲】</note><app n="0031001"><lem wit="【大】">止</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">上</rdg></app>宿。亦各依本方&CB00594;立八旗。執旗
<lb n="0031a03" ed="T"/>人燒安息香。以諸素淨飲食供養。本方旗幡
<lb n="0031a04" ed="T"/>大將於中止宿。燒沈水香真妙上者。亦以淨
<lb n="0031a05" ed="T"/>食供養。作一石不動尊明王像。高十二指畫
<lb n="0031a06" ed="T"/>彼人形。及<note n="0031002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">書＝畫【甲】</note><app n="0031002"><lem wit="【大】">書</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">畫</rdg></app>彼姓<note n="0031003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔名〕－【甲】</note><app n="0031003"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>。以此石像當上<note n="0031004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">厭＝壓&M062303;【原】</note><app n="0031004"><lem wit="【大】">厭</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【Ｂ】">壓</rdg></app>
<lb n="0031a07" ed="T"/>之。如是不久自當消滅<note n="0031005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔矣〕－【甲】</note><app n="0031005"><lem wit="【大】">矣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>。</p></div1>
<lb n="0031a08" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>不動明王安鎮家國<note n="0031006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法＋（一卷）【甲】，此下甲本有大治三年五月十八日高野山奧院實海本</note><app n="0031006"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">法一卷</rdg></app><note n="0031006" type="rest" place="foot">此下甲本有大治三年五月十八日高野山奧院實海本</note></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0031a09" ed="T"/><div1 type="W"><p id="pT21p0031a0901"><note n="0031007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以下甲本無之</note><note n="0031007" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>以下甲本無之</note>八家祕錄云。不動明王安鎮家國等法一
<lb n="0031a10" ed="T"/>卷金剛智三藏付王<note n="0031008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無＝光&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0031008" resp="【原】" corr="光">無</sic>海錄外。</p>
<lb n="0031a11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0031a1101">享和元辛酉天後秋月索此本於洛東智積
<lb n="0031a12" ed="T"/>教院更校餘本點國字鏤版。</p>
<lb n="0031a13" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0031a1301">　　和州豐山長谷歡喜院沙門快道誌</p>
<lb n="0031a14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0031a1401">　文政三年庚辰秋八月二十七日以秀陽
<lb n="0031a15" ed="T"/>闍梨本墨校了　龍肝</p>
<lb n="0031a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0031a1601">　文政四年辛巳秋九月二十三日以板橋
<lb n="0031a17" ed="T"/>日曜寺宣雄比丘本朱再校了</p></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>